<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Housekeeping - Panel Order Taker</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/font-awesome@4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            hotel: {
              dark: '#0F2B48',
              primary: '#2D5B7C',
              light: '#E8F0F5',
              accent: '#F2994A',
              success: '#27AE60',
              danger: '#E74C3C',
              neutral: '#F8FAFC'
            }
          },
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ['Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Arial', 'sans-serif']
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-hotel-neutral min-h-screen">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-3 py-4 max-w-3xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md mb-5 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="bg-hotel-dark text-white px-5 py-4 flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <i class="fa fa-headphones text-2xl"></i>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-lg font-bold">Panel Order Taker</h1>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Selamat datang, <strong><%= user.nama %></strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/logout" class="bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition flex items-center gap-1">
          <i class="fa fa-sign-out"></i> Keluar
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Konten Utama -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-check-square-o text-5xl text-hotel-primary mb-4"></i>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-hotel-dark mb-2">Modul Pesanan & Koordinasi</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Halaman ini digunakan untuk mencatat permintaan tamu, mengatur jadwal, dan mengoordinasikan kebutuhan kebersihan kamar.</p>
      <div class="bg-hotel-light p-4 rounded-md text-left text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p class="font-medium mb-2">Informasi:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Semua permintaan tamu akan diteruskan ke tim Room Attendant</li>
          <li>Status kamar dapat diperbarui secara real-time</li>
          <li>Laporan dapat dilihat dan diunduh oleh Supervisor</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
